, I could call this helper via reflection or maybe an interface. I can define the helper in test sources implementing a parent interface. If the helper implements `Runnable`, I can cast it if the child delegates `java.lang.Runnable` to the parent. I could make `IsolatedTaskAdapterExercise` a public static final class in the test jar.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_03f19f5e1c5d66c80169fbbe2d28788196b3164cb0d69cc291\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp-75mCX-1a3vxGe89a_SRsW2ojF_1GHcvwi_wmM10ESvxWvRLVWKQD_0INbOkAwrn_lspLd5uVxYCZt9y4ouwNbewyxMvGnekgy1gU1IYASsOwggPb1fpU6iiElS-5SzBT1-s_JXhrxesiJfmbViHjQ_NemWEPCFQY3PH8BFnvbxoQCeNRcw-6UZ9GU5cG1zFtUbCPVnoYqRjaV9axvMKtYqp8o0DNnmXOWaqYBe6VdfVAjd9DstV5ldA0ZGjdPA3MsFQyHGxnM64VxWnqYteIS-AcMylgExP8Cwqw_M_NXOlBjo-DeWf0Ubd2laqi3wLkY0RRCG1SywmPtaUzokJn90xQVDknDpUJmBF0jqJunuu4R0BWIZs2CHDurB-vWWugiJFw4oxTMC52dB1mu1TC4Afcg1HLEEo81Vyz0tF4HhR63cZ8lXchMVSGWj9VEhvtHf4t8oNYMYyiLrzIaFyBzeo-yI-nInO1DClqOTDIITAh540OsjY_rWirDavTuUeH3HhlJ5tT0_2c8EggvzDZW4dHb7tKCKbWsEVIQLzd7Ddi1-uALIiajVPDASx61eWCRmLYu8khOXMSnheiCWEtTA5BtVPV1smKbjB1JyS3XC2i3tq09niCjN7HBc6q7sgQhqc8l-e79m3bXFuNMLb-0GmuvKZoo7TpBSWq8P4XT2XN3KwW4cpVptOJ6mXOCrULLfwJpvUT0YHM-rmRoVCAkWpEFGiqQYExLKt0A_8aVx1SKsHlcLBUEwDkJCa8ZpGb-sf4VjbsETpvDYHfN7xZKCLzp4Nhhy12SHYOMsj68EmNPFuZRK6jzmH1d8XzlEi0Nnux9oZC9syRuOIj7v55N2BymcP-DyPUsbxqXT3Lrm6w5n687x8d4sCwX2Zc_dnHLICWibUB9WuvTb70HUUxID0s2lIpEqXiK5Oy8gNHMv9l0U7KBFAA_VX4eAiwRP9AOauIh6qWzkXl-rwCfJ_J4iwuaDSAiUl_A4Hd-V3eGo6hAfQgMZQgBTr3awOhc7gIOzpKfxJWi2S3qlkAroefEoLR9ACsV1e2oGR3uBZsAoaVQ7OD--nrlUEOdiIFwVCoykLml5jH4sypZ_opvLm-IJ69e7_xwJyTRrHhnM7ZC-Gb_Mzz-HtChe0Kmqk7r7hoE-9Lqp2cy00p-U3ZDCyJ7cyhxkBn3_reAFsrKtIPXSrkAUpIQn_ZJcUWcUXak4vc-8ceyYjlTI1_zvfNPDrx2WVO3DeoYfc9Phy6jaHmEWsHAEWnhDAxm_CdbyYAXGxEtqglU-YVNfSboOV6WuUp8tAQMU0dCGdUqPDNNpVIllJeRHMAiZhjD--IUU7eCOYEfh7cKqGz61IEzJnvT93uvJZkxbn3uPJm6QEgRe4Nz-xcxngFqoqW1-fkqwjcRjCl90kfahe4FIE5OZaTIq6zprp4DjZZ1KcZYsQsC_wK_UIh6S7shtxeM37jO9OwrkH608m90xc6qIxpb1tfBb_EssQBceTRzGfNUhPEv4z3L1rkRj