[assistant] Updated `tests/src/ant/ant/1.6/src/test/java/ant/ant/TaskAdapterTest.java` to add an isolated-loader exercise for `TaskAdapter`.
[assistant] 
[assistant] What changed:
[assistant] - Added `executesProxyTaskFromIsolatedLoader()`.
[assistant] - The test loads `TaskAdapter` through a child-first `URLClassLoader`.
